# AI change log (memory)

When an implementation **succeeds** and the diff materially affects **architecture, component system, public routes/SEO, CI, or future API posture**, append **exactly two lines** to [`.cursor/history/CHLOG-AI.md`](.cursor/history/CHLOG-AI.md):

- Line 1: `YYYY-MM-DD —` one-sentence summary
- Line 2: optional scope (paths or areas)

Skip copy-only tweaks and one-line bugfixes.
